        <p><strong>Windows Server 2008</strong> (sometimes abbreviated as "<strong>Win2K8</strong>" or "<strong>W2K8</strong>") is one of <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Microsoft Windows', 'OS'); ?> server line of operating systems. Released to manufacturing on 4 February 2008, and officially released on 27 February 2008, it is the successor to <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Windows Server 2003', 'WIS'); ?>, released nearly five years earlier. A second release, named <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Windows Server 2008 R2', 'WIS'); ?>, was released to manufacturing on 22 July 2009.</p>
